entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have been inoculated by Zahara Cody.
entries.journal_entry_description: Find the person responsible for inoculating survivors.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go to the quarantine zone entrance to gain access.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Go to the refugee camp and find out who is inoculating survivors.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Have Zahara Cody inoculate you for the mission. The anti-virus she provides will only last for a short time, though, so seek medical droids in the area to renew your anti-virus.
